<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <div class="container" style="max-width: 600px; text-align: center; padding: 4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div class="card">
      <div style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background: var(--secondary); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; font-size: 2.5rem;">
        ✅
      </div>

      <h1 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--primary);">
        Payment Successful!
      </h1>
      
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
        Your payment has been received and held securely in escrow. The farmer will be notified to dispatch your order.
      </p>

      <div style="background: #dbeafe; padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: left;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: #1e40af;">
          What happens next?
        </h3>
        <ol style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #1e40af; margin-left: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
          <li>Farmer receives notification to prepare your order</li>
          <li>Your payment is held securely (escrow protection)</li>
          <li>Farmer marks order as "Dispatched" when shipped</li>
          <li>You confirm delivery after receiving the order</li>
          <li>Payment is released to the farmer</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/buyer/orders" class="btn btn-primary">View My Orders</a>
        <a href="/buyer/dashboard" class="btn btn-outline">Browse More Crops</a>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-top: 2rem;">
        You can track your order status in "My Orders" section.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
